light_footmen_flavor:1 "#F 这些足轻由“地侍”组成，往往来自于贫穷武士与富农之间的灰色地带，他们战时充军，平时务农。#!" <"#F These ashigaru were composed of "land servants" who often came from the gray area between poor samurai and rich peasants. They served in the army during war and worked as farmers in peacetime. #!"> #NT!
bowmen_flavor:0 "#F 熟练的弓箭手箭矢布满天空，摧毁敌人的先头部队。#!" <"#F Skilled archers fill the sky with arrows and destroy the enemy's vanguard. #!"> #NT!
crossbowmen_flavor:0 "#F 虽然重新装填需要时间，但火绳枪使用方便，可以从远距离贯穿大部分的铠甲。#!" <"#F Although reloading takes time, the matchlock gun is easy to use and can penetrate most armor from a long distance. #!"> #NT!
armored_footmen_flavor:0 "#F 装备精良且训练有素的武士，擅长收割杂兵。#!" <"#F A well-equipped and well-trained warrior who is good at harvesting miscellaneous soldiers. #!"> #NT!
armored_horsemen_flavor:0 "#F 全副武装的骑马武士，决定了平原战斗的胜败。#!" <"#F Heavily armed horseback warriors determine the outcome of battles on the plains. #!"> #NT!
onager_flavor:0 "#F 由许多排列在地面上的盾牌组成。保护士兵免受敌人箭矢的攻击。#!" <"#F  consists of many shields arranged on the ground. Protect soldiers from enemy arrows. #!"> #NT!
mangonel_flavor:0 "#F 用木头和竹子组合而成的箭楼。用于侦察和压制城内。#!" <"#F A watchtower made of wood and bamboo. Used for reconnaissance and suppression within the city. #!"> #NT!
trebuchet_flavor:0 "#F 把竹子捆起来当盾。不仅能挡住箭矢，还可以抵挡火绳枪的子弹。#!" <"#F Tie up bamboo to use as a shield. Not only can it block arrows, but it can also withstand matchlock bullets. #!"> #NT!
bombard_flavor:0 "#F 战国时代的大炮。虽然价格昂贵且数量稀少，但可以轻松炸开防御工事。#!" <"#F A cannon from the Warring States Period. Although expensive and rare, they can easily blast through defenses. #!"> #NT!

